text:
Divya Rao Mar . 16 . 2017 
Divyanka Tripathi and Vivek Dahiya tied the knot earlier last year and the two have since then been on multiple little trips together, and always show us snippets thanks to Instagram. This time for Holi, the couple went away to Punjab and spent time in a no-network area aka in a forest. Check out their photos. A post shared by Vivek Dahiya (@officialvivekdahiya) on Mar 13, 2017 at 11:07pm PDT A post shared by Vivek Dahiya (@officialvivekdahiya) on Mar 15, 2017 at 12:28am PDT 
Haha so cute, these two! 1
